\n<Dwarf Axeman>If they e'er try somethin' like that again,\. our weapons are ready!
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Nothing to see here,\. kittie.\.\. Just a buncha corpses.
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Had to block the main road he'e.\.\. Too many of them snouts around...\.\.\. and at night...
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Had to block the main road he'e.\.\. Too many of them snouts around...\.\.\. and at night...
The cat didn't have a good feeling about this.\.\. Considering the last times she'd heard a noise down here...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Ooooh,\. if you're getting yourself into trouble again,\. girl,\. I'm gonna give you such a pinch...!\.\.

Already with low hopes,\. Neneko takes off running.\.\. This time things were really loud.\.\. There's a full blown battle going on somewhere,\. and she needed to know if her instincts were wrong!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Oh boy...\.\.\. Shina,\. what in the world did you get yourself into NOW...\.\.\.
Against all of her hopes and wishes that for once her gut was incorrect,\. Neneko's fears were confirmed the moment she came across the battle.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>Haaaahhh...!!!\.\. You want some!?\.\. Come get some!!!\.\. There's plenty meat to go around!!\.\.
There Shina was,\. going on what Neneko could only describe as a rampage.\.\.
It looked like there were kobolds AND dwarves here.\.\. Neneko had the feeling most of the bodies on the floor were because of her.\.\.
This place isn't dwarf or kobold territory...\.\.\. contested ground,\. in other words.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Ugh...\.\.\. Shina,\. what the hell?\.\. Why're you getting involved in this stupid feud?\.\.
She isn't helping either side.\.\. From what it looked like,\. these guys were already in a fight and she just decided to charge in and wreck things for no reason.\.\.
Seeing her swing that battleaxe around and moo like a crazed bull seeing red...\.\.\.
Shina was sweating,\. panting,\. yet her eyes were red with battlelust.\.\. She didn't even seem to realize her own exhaustion.\.\.
And the enemies were still coming.\.\. It looked like both sides of the fight had decided to focus on the Beast in the center of the fight,\. smashing everything indiscriminately.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Shina,\. you idiot,\. get out of there...\.\.\.
But Neneko could already tell Shina wasn't thinking about the odds or herself.\.\. It hardly looked like she was thinking of anything.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I've never seen you in a rage like this...\.\.\. it's scary...\.\.\.
Feral.\.\. That was the only way to describe the Shina Neneko was looking at.\.\. A crazed animal that only saw threats all around her and was responding with her "Fight" instincts.\.\.
If this kept up,\. then the pinkette would surely get overwhelmed.\.\.
She'd managed to make herself an enemy of both of the big factions here,\. and if she stayed in the middle of that mess then one or the other would strike her once she'd tired herself out...\.\.\.
There was no doubt in Neneko's mind how this was going to play out.\.\. The situation was getting worse.\.\. Shina was getting more and more exhausted...\.\.\.
And her foes could clearly see it.\.\.
Neneko didn't hesitate.\.\. With a sprint and a leap she dashed past the enemy lines,\. giving a startled meow as she ducked under Shina's axe swing.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Shina,\. damn it,\. it's me!\.\. Neneko!\.\. Your bestest friend in the world!?\.\.
Neneko yowls,\. avoiding a headbutt,\. grabbing Shina's shoulders and shaking her.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Calm down,\. girl!\.\. You're in the middle of a warzone!\.\. What are you doing here!?\.\.
It's like she was seeing red.\.\. The girl barely even looked Neneko's way.\.\. Neneko had to duck and slip behind Shina as she kept swinging her axe wildly to keep the soldiers at bay.\.\.
Her swings were getting clumsier,\. slower.\.\.
She wasn't listening to reason,\. and Neneko quickly realized that now SHE was in the center of this mess too.\.\.
Not a good position to be in.\.\.
Neneko needed to act fast,\. or they'd both get buried in way too many pointy objects...\.\.\.
Neneko bares her claws.\.\. Shina doesn't respond to her comment,\. not that she expected her to.\.\.
Crazy bull strength or not,\. Neneko could still outspeed Shina any day.\.\. From this close...\.\.\. she could get a hit in no matter what.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Come to your senses,\. you stupid cow!!\.\.
Neneko leaps in and strikes,\. slashing Shina's exposed arm and causing the girl to nearly drop her battleaxe in pain and alarm.\.\.
She grips her injury,\. turning with blazing anger in her eyes,\. only to falter,\. a look of confusion and betrayal (and still quite a bit of anger) filling her expression.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>Neneko!?\.\. What the hell are you doing-\.-\.
Shina gasps.\.\. Neneko wasn't done with her attack,\. clearly,\. as the pinkette was suddenly slapped across the face,\. her eyes flickering as she processed the sting on her cheek.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I should be the one asking that!!!\.\. What the hell are YOU doing,\. Shina!?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>No,\. shut up!\.\. I'll tell you what you're doing!\.\. You're picking fights like some lunatic for no reason!\.\. Did you forget about why we're down here!?\.\.

<
[1]>
[2]'s waiting for us down in one of the lower Stratums!\.\. There's nothing for you up here,\. and this fight's got nothing to do with us!!\.\.
Shina was paralyzed,\. a hand drifting to her cheek,\. the grip on her axe loose.\.\.
Suddenly she shakes her head,\. gasping and looking around.\.\.
The pinkette moves,\. wrapping her arm around Neneko's waist.\.\.
And with ridiculous strength,\. Shina kicks off of the ground and leaps straight over a line of dwarves with Neneko in tow,\. before dashing away from the battlefield,\. never looking back.\.\.
It's only several minutes after the sound of conflict has faded away that they finally stop running.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>...\.\.\. Hahh...\.\.\. I honestly can't even defend myself to that...\.\.\.
Shina collapses to her knees.\.\. She looks completely exhausted.\.\. Neneko moves over to check on her.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You finally get it out of your system...?\.\.
\n<\n[4]>I...\.\.\. yeah,\. I...\.\.\. I think I did...\.\.\. honestly,\. I just felt so...\.\.\. hotheaded and angry...\.\.\.
She purses her lips,\. looking down.\.\.

<
[4]>...\.\.\. Thanks,\. Neneko.\.\. I really did just lose my way back there...\.\.\. if you didn't get my head back on straight,\. I don't even know what I would've done...\.\.\. and then 
[2] would've...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hmph.\.\. Just doing my job.\.\. \BST[1]I'm used to getting things through your thick skull.\.\.
Neneko pokes one of Shina's horns.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Even if your skull's,\. like,\. way thicker now.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>Hah...\.\.\. spose so...\.\.\. phew...\.\.\. guess I deserved that slap too...\.\.\.
Shina stands up,\. slowly,\. her legs shaking.\.\.

<
[4]>Yeah,\. I...\.\.\. yeah.\.\. Prolly better not to rest out here...\.\.\. Nene,\. about 
[2]...\.\.\. is he really...?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>...\.\.\. Yeah.\.\. The Hole...\.\.\. it goes deeper than this.\.\. Way deeper.\.\. \BST[2]Whoever took him...\.\.\. didn't stop at this floor.\.\. They kept going down.\.\.
Shina grimaces,\. leaning on her axe.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>...\.\.\. Alright.\.\. We'll...\.\.\. just have to keep going,\. then.\.\. Together,\. this time.\.\. No more...\.\.\. uh,\. doing things on my own.\.\. I'll make sure to remember that.\.\.
They stare at each other,\. before Shina gives a shy,\. tired smile.\.\. Neneko can't help but smile back,\. relief on her face.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>Thank you,\. Nene.\.\. For looking out for me like always,\. haha.\.\. I...\.\.\. I owe you for this.\.\. I'll be looking out for you too,\. okay?\.\. Be careful around here.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You don't gotta remind me,\. Shina...\.\.\. you just be careful too from now on.\.\. \BST[1]You're gonna make me lose some hairs,\. worrying me like that.\.\.
Shina nods,\. and claims Neneko for a hug before picking up her axe.\.\.
\n<\n[4]>I'm going to keep looking around after I find a place to rest for a while.\.\. I'll just slow you down like this.\.\. \BST[3]But I'll be there if you need me,\. I promise!\.\.
The Pinkette waves,\. then makes her exit.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Looking out for me now,\. huh?\.\. Shina's really become something lately...\.\.\.
Neneko crouches low.\.\. Shina doesn't respond to her comment.\.\. She doesn't even acknowledge her.\.\.
It hurts a bit,\. knowing that,\. but Neneko can't linger here.\.\. She couldn't let Shina drag her down with her if she was going to be like this.\.\. Not when she still had a mission.\.\.
Neneko leaps out of the crossfire,\. dashing out of the middle of the battlefield before she can get caught up in that mess.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Tsk...\.\.\. stupid Shina.\.\. \BST[2]You better not get yourself hurt or killed or \N[2]'ll never let me hear the end of it when we go back home...\.\.\.
Neneko doesn't look back.\.\. She really didn't want to see Shina right now.\.\. Nor how tired and slow she looked while those soldiers were approaching.\.\.
The girl could probably take care of herself anyway.\.\. Especially with all that crazy strength she was suddenly packing.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Mind your own business,\. Neneko.\.\. You can't wait around for her or deal with this place's problems.\.\. I gotta keep moving.\.\.
The cat shakes her head,\. trying not to think about a head of pink as she put the battlefield behind her and made as much distance as she could.\.\.
